high_descs: Turn around to walk to the bathtub across the room.
Pick up a bar of soap from the bathtub ledge.
Turn towards the bathtub.
Put the bar of soap in the bathtub.
Make a left to walk to the trash can next to the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap from the trash can,
Turn left to walk to the bathtub.
Place the other bar of soap in the bathtub.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap into the bathtub.

high_descs: Turn around to your left and go to the end of the bathtub beside the white towel hanging on the wall.
Pick up the bar of soap behind the candle off the end of the bathtub.
Turn around to the bathtub.
Place the bar if soap beside the rag in the bottom of the bathtub.
Turn to your right and go the right side of the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap out if the red can on the floor beside the sink.
Take the bar of soap back over to the bathtub.
Place bar of soap beside the other one down inside the bathtub.
anns.task_desc: Place two bars of soap into the bathtub.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the left side of the bath tub across the room.
Pick up the pink sponge on the left ledge of the bath tub.
Move over right to the bath tub.
Place the pink sponge inside the bath tub.
Turn right and go to the red trash can between the toilet and the sink.
Take the pink sponge out of the trash can.
Turn left and go back to the bath tub.
Place the pink sponge on the right side of the first sponge.
anns.task_desc: Move two pink sponges into the bath tub.
